name: Spacewarp
description:
A / D or  ← / → to MOVE

W or  ↑ to  BOOST

🖱️ or 2 / 4 / 6 / 8 to WARP

R to RESTART

The version above represents an additional three hours of polishing and small fixes, clocking in at a total of just under six hours.

Both the three hour and six hour versions are available to download for comparison.

Made in two hours, fifty-five minutes for Trijam 121.

This is by no means a finished work. It features two very simplistic levels to display the basic mechanics. Each level can be finished, after which the player will return to the starting screen.
